# Day-6 Project

## Description
A simple Python project demonstrating modular programming, input handling, and basic business logic.

## Project Structure



day-6/
├── core/ # Business logic
│ └── logic.py
├── utils/ # Helper functions (formatting, messages)
│ └── helpers.py
└── main.py # Entry point, coordinates core and utils

## Technologies Used
- **Python 3.11** – core programming language  
- **Docker** – containerization for running the project anywhere  
- **Modular Code Structure** – separates business logic (`core`) from helpers (`utils`)  
- **CI-Friendly Input Handling** – supports interactive input and automation environments (like GitHub Actions)

## How to Run

### Locally
```bash
python main.py

## Using Docker
```bash
docker build -t day6-app .
docker run --name day-6 -it day6-app